Step 1 : Start
Step 2 : Enter Number of Productions
Step 3 : Read the Productions
Step 4 : For each production repeat steps 5
Step 5 : Check RHS of Production
Step 6 : Check weather the production is single digit. If not, go to next production
Step 7 : Replace RHS with the digit
Step 8 : Check the next subsequent lines
Step 9 : Check RHS of the production of the subsequent lines
Step 10 : If RHS does not contain the character to replace, go to step 8
Step 11 : Replace RHS character with the digit
Step 12 : Display the new optimized code
Step 13 : Stop
